item.title: Allstar source- How do i a Commands list?
item.dc:creator: @droidmobile droidmobile@yahoo.com
item.description:
@droidmobile wrote:

Add this somewhere in your client.java

public void commands() { sendQuest("Command List", 8144); clearQuestInterface(); sendQuest("Normal Player Commands", 8147); sendQuest("::changepassword (newpass)", 8148); sendQuest("::empty (emptys your inv)", 8149); sendQuest("::skill (teleports you to Skillzone)", 8150); sendQuest("MORE TO COME!", 8151); sendQuest("------------------------------------", 8153); sendQuest("Donator Commands", 8155); sendQuest("::yell (message)", 8154); sendQuest("::dzone (teleports you to Donator Zone)", 8155); sendQuest("MORE TO COME!", 8156); sendQuest("-", 8158); sendQuest("Moderator Commands", 8159); sendQuest("::staffzone (Teleports you to Staffzone)", 8160); sendQuest("::mute/::unmute (username)", 8161); sendQuest("::dropreset (resets the drops)", 8162); sendQuest("::xteleto (username)", 8163); sendQuest("::jail/::unjail (username) - jails/unjails a player", 8164); sendQuestSomething(8143); showInterface(8134); flushOutStream(); }

You also need to add this above/under another command already in the client.java

if(command.startsWith("commands")){ commands(); }
